"""
Memory Retrieval Helper - v1.2
- Two-stage retrieval (pinned first, semantic fallback)
- Stage 2: OpenViking CLI integration for semantic search
- Tombstone double-filter
- Retrieval audit logging with sampling
- Superseded redirect handling
- Deterministic sorting and budget limits
- Separates recall events from use events
"""

